div.div: Tensei Shitara Slime Datta Ken 2nd Season Part 2

The second cour of Tensei Shitara Slime Datta Ken 2nd Season. The nation of Tempest is in a festive mood after successfully overcoming the surprise attack from the Falmuth Army and the Western Holy Church. Beyond the festivities lies a meeting between Tempest and its allies to decide the future of the Nation of Monsters. The aftermath of the Falmuth invasion, Milim Nava's suspicious behavior, and the disappearance of Demon Lord Carrionâ€”the problems seem to keep on piling up. Rimuru Tempest, now awakened as a "True Demon Lord," decides to go on the offensive against Clayman. With the fully revived "Storm Dragon" Veldora, "Ultimate Skill" Raphael, and other powerful comrades, the ruler of the Tempest is confident in taking down his enemies one by one until he can face the man pulling the strings.

The second season of Yakusoku no Neverland. Fifteen children escape Grace Field House, a false paradise, hoping for a chance at freedom. Instead, they encounter plants and animals they have never before seen, and are chased by demons. The outside world is so beautiful, and yet is almost too cruel to face. Even so, the children refuse to give up. They are guided in their search for better lives only by a message from Minerva and a pen Norman left behind in order to fulfill their promise to return to the House to save those of their family who are still trapped within.
(Source: Aniplex of America) Note: Episode 1 streamed early on Amazon Prime on Jan 7, 2021. The regular TV broadcast started on Jan 8, 2021.
Otome Game no Mob desura naindaga
Comedy, Fantasy, Romance, Slice of Life

Taichi was reincarnated as Isaac, an apprentice gardener in the world of an otome game. But, looking back, Isaac wasn't even part of the game... This is the story of the interweaving lives of the Duke's daughter, Lydia, and a boy who isn't even an NPC.
(Source: MANGA UP!)
Action, Drama, Fantasy, Mystery, Psychological, Sci-Fi

After being beaten up by bullies, high school senior Yi-Yeon Kang wakes up from a coma, only to find the world in ruins from an alien invasion. The streets around him are littered and empty, with bullies out looking for their next prey. As he navigates this new world, despite being too weak, he is determined to find and save his friend Young-Lin. Between bullies, aliens and this post-apocalyptic reality, he'll do all he can to survive... and to bring down those out to get him.
(Source: Tapas)

div.span: Turbulent Adventurers are Introverted, Observant, Feeling, Prospecting and Turbulent. Adventurers are flexible and charming, always ready to explore and experience something new. They tend to have open minds, approaching life, new experiences, and people with grounded warmth.
Mostly Introverted. Likely prefers fewer, yet deep and meaningful, social interactions and feels drawn to calmer environments.
Mostly Observant. Likely pragmatic and down-to-earth, with a strong focus on what is happening or very likely to happen.
Mostly Feeling. Likely values emotional expression and sensitivity, prioritizing empathy, social harmony, and cooperation.
Mostly Prospecting. Likely very good at improvising and adapting. Tends to be flexible and values novelty above stability.
Mostly Turbulent. Likely self-conscious, sensitive to stress, success-driven, perfectionistic, and eager to improve.
